Package: ksr-cli
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CLI tool for Kafka Schema Registry
 ksr-cli is a comprehensive command-line interface for managing
 Kafka Schema Registry. It provides commands to get, create, delete,
 and manage schemas, subjects, and configurations.
 .
 Features:
  * Cross-platform support (Linux, macOS, Windows)
  * JSON/YAML output formats
  * Configuration file support
  * Shell completion (bash/zsh/fish)
  * Authentication support
  * Comprehensive error handling
 .
 This package contains the ksr-cli binary and supporting files.
